entries.femaleVariant: Now this... What, I gotta pay for all my gear outta pocket? Why don't I just pay my own wages, too?
Kid, you got a lotta learnin' to do. You wanna work, gotta lay out some eds first.
But how much? It's the second time this year! They want me to buy a new uniform, let 'em gimme a raise first!
Kid, you gotta earn your eddies. Go hungry a couple days a month, you'll save up enough.
Heard it's healthy, too. Like detox or somethin'.
Yeah. Then I pass out on the job, they fire me anyway.
